{"tid":2176439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」2021 馬拉松又延期","createTime":"2020-08-27T05:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T05:52:00.000Z","uid":289694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cae0bf02cedd50ef41ec4d566d4c056793198a08","tid":2176439,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"Dear Runners,<br />\n <br />\nPublic health and safety is always our top priority. Due to the uncertainty around the COVID-19 epidemic situation, the Standard Chartered Hong Kong Marathon originally scheduled for 24 January 2021 (Sunday) will be postponed. The Organiser is now actively working with relevant parties to make appropriate arrangement. Please stay tuned for further details to be published on our website (<a href=\"http://www.hkmarathon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmarathon.com&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=24ad473b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkmarathon.com</a>) and our Facebook fan page (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hkmarathon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkmarathon&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=aae6bbca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/hkmarathon</a>).<br />\n <br />\nThank you for your continued support!<br />\n <br />\nRegards,<br />\nRegistration and Runners&rsquo; Communication Office<br />\nStandard Chartered Hong Kong Marathon<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n親愛的跑手：<br />\n <br />\n公眾健康一直是我們的首要考慮。鑒於本港疫情尚未穩定，原定於2021年1月24日(星期日)舉行之渣打香港馬拉松賽事將會延期。大會現正積極與相關部門研究另訂日期舉辦賽事的安排。<a href=\"http://請密切留意大會網頁www.hkmarathon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AB%8B%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%95%99%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81www.hkmarathon.com&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=0d94eafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">請密切留意大會網頁www.hkmarathon.com</a> <a href=\"http://及Facebook專頁www.facebook.com/hkmarathon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%8AFacebook%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81www.facebook.com%2Fhkmarathon&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=4789aeb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">及Facebook專頁www.facebook.com/hkmarathon</a> 公佈，有關賽事的最新消息。<br />\n <br />\n感謝 閣下對渣打香港馬拉松的支持！<br />\n <br />\n渣打香港馬拉松<br />\n報名及跑手通訊辦事處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係未正式光復香港前，應該都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccfe9ad8ca1ad703dc1e26fff3b626b4ac44024","tid":2176439,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17db0b17e90937974965de29bb676c15b9747ca2","tid":2176439,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"416c395395318a1e22bff06bbb7488d33a674932","tid":2176439,"uid":33408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"驚有班搞事友跑跑下堵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416717253a8926ca67a633196c321198fcf207b6","tid":2176439,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"416c395395318a1e22bff06bbb7488d33a674932","tid":2176439,"uid":33408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"驚有班搞事友跑跑下堵路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"同咪如果到時叫光復香港，唔知會唔會舉紫旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"